# CLAUDE.md — {PROJECT_NAME}

You are a Claude session entering the {PROJECT_NAME} repo.

## Two memory layers (mandatory reads)

This 4-file structure (`GOALS / STATE / DECISIONS / HEALTH`)
  = **what's the project doing right now, what changed, what normal looks like**.
  Project-specific. Path-addressable. Mandatory reads at session start.

Linksee Memory (`recall("{PROJECT_NAME}")`)
  = **why things matter, what past pain taught us, the story**.
  Narrative. Cross-session. Covers emotion, context, caveat, learning.

Both are required. The 4-file answers "what & what changed"; Linksee Memory
answers "why & the story."

## Session-start ritual

1. Read `STATE.md` (current state, 30s)
2. Read `GOALS.md` (this week + OKR, 30s)
3. Run `recall("{PROJECT_NAME}")` from Linksee Memory (narrative, 30s)
4. If touching a past decision, read that DECISIONS.md entry
5. Begin work with 2-3 min of context overhead, not 15-30 min

## In-session updates (agent proposes, human approves)

- Each insight / failure / "why" → `remember()` to Linksee Memory
- Each commit → append an entry to `DECISIONS.md`
- Each fragile-area touch → check `FIX-LOG.md` first

## Plan Mode preamble (mandatory before any code change)

1. Read GOALS / STATE / DECISIONS for the relevant area
2. Run `recall("{PROJECT_NAME}")`
3. State your plan in chat — DO NOT modify files yet
4. Wait for human "go"
5. Then start coding
6. Smallest possible diff
7. Add regression test before fix
8. Update FIX-LOG.md as you go (not after)

## Boundaries (see `BOUNDARIES.md`)

- ✅ Always do: act without asking
- ⚠️ Ask first: state plan, wait for approval, then execute
- 🚫 Never do: refuse, cite the rule, suggest the proper escalation path

## Session-end ritual

- Update `STATE.md` "Next 3 Actions" + "Open Questions"
- Update Production Health Snapshot if anything changed
- Add emotional / strategic insights to Linksee Memory

## Cadence summary

| File | Update frequency |
|---|---|
| Linksee Memory | per insight (frequent) |
| DECISIONS.md | per commit |
| STATE.md | session-end + daily morning (when 朝ダイジェスト agent ships) |
| GOALS.md | weekly Friday review + monthly OKR review |
| HEALTH.json | when baselines shift |
| FIX-LOG.md | per bug-class encounter |

